value.title: Change CoinEx Chain Proposal Voting Period to 7 days
value.description:
Proposal on shortening the voting period of the CoinEx Chain proposal
The voting period of 14 natural days is too long, which is not good to the development of CoinEx Chain. Therefore, the CETDAC propose to change the voting period from 14 natural days to 7 natural days.

关于调整CoinE Chain 提案投票周期缩短的提案
14个自然日的投票周期过于冗长，不利于CoinEx Chain发展。因此CETDAC节点提议，将投票周期从14个自然日到7个自然日。

value.title: Proposal on reducing the cost of CoinEx Chain DEX coin issuance
value.description:
现有的CoinEx Chain DEX发币成本极高，严重影响发币体验以及整体发展。
因此，联合 喵星电台发起关于降低CoinEx Chain DEX发币成本的提案：发行2字母token成本从100k CET降低至10k CET，发行3 & 3+字母token的成本从10k CET 降低至 1k CET，请大家支持，谢谢！

The current CoinEx Chain DEX issuance cost is extremely high, which seriously affects the issuance experience and overall development.
Therefore, the and propose to reduce the cost of CoinEx Chain DEX coin issuance as below:
1. the cost of issuing a 2-letter token was reduced from 100k CET to 5k CET
2. the cost of issuing a 3 & 3+ letter token was 10k CET reduced to 500 CET.
please support , highly appreciate！

value.title: 关于降低CoinEx Chain DEX创建交易对费用的提案
value.description:
现有的CoinEx Chain DEX创建交易对的成本极高，严重影响发币体验以及整体发展。

因此，CETDAC社区发起关于降低CoinEx Chain DEX发币成本的提案：由10000cet上币费降低为100cet。感谢大家的支持，谢谢！

value.title: Proposal on reducing the number of CET stake of CoinEx Chain nodes
value.description:
At present, due to the high number of on-chain stake that have become CoinEx Chain nodes, it has prevented some high-quality institutions and organizations that hold fewer coins but want to become nodes to join, which greatly reduces the ecological construction efficiency of CoinEx Chain.

Therefore, in order to encourage more credible, resourceful and reputable institutions and organizations to join and participate in the CoinEx Chain ecological co-construction, ViaWallet hereby launches a proposal to reduce the number of node stake: the number of node pledges is reduced from the current 5 million CET to 1 million CET.

I hope everyone will actively support and build the CoinEx Chain ecosystem together!


关于降低CoinEx Chain节点CET质押数量提案

目前，由于成为CoinEx Chain节点的链上质押数较高，阻碍了一些持币量较少但想成为节点的优质机构和组织的加入，这样大大降低了CoinEx Chain的生态建设效率。

因此，为了鼓励更多有公信力、有资源、信誉良好的机构和组织加入并参与CoinEx Chain生态共建中，ViaWallet特此发起降低节点质押数量提案：节点质押数量由目前500万CET降至100万CET。

希望大家踊跃支持，一起共建CoinEx Chain生态！

value.name: Filecoin
value.description:
星际文件系统IPFS（InterPlanetary File System）是一个面向全球的、点对点的分布式版本文件系统，目标是为了补充（甚至是取代）目前统治互联网的超文本传输协议（HTTP），将所有具有相同文件系统的计算设备连接在一起。原理用基于内容的地址替代基于域名的地址，也就是用户寻找的不是某个地址而是储存在某个地方的内容，不需要验证发送者的身份，而只需要验证内容的哈希，通过这样可以让网页的速度更快、更安全、更健壮、更持久。

Filecoin是在IPFS其上的激励层，通过token激励模式在IPFS上构建了一个去中心化存储市场。
